        "subject": "LU-1745 test: Support new IR stares for recovery-small test 105",
        "message": "LU-1745 test: Support new IR stares for recovery-small test 105\n\nLustre version 2.3 will report new IR states than what is\nreported in Lustre 2.2. This patch ensures that the regression\ntest running on Lustre 2.2 clients with 2.3+ servers will pass.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: Iaa40131e11ba19b3dba46ca80f5ac2fb66460a54\n"
